Name
    no-pool-nginx

Description
    This is a patch file to nginx source. It replaces nginx's pool machanism 
    with plain malloc&free to help tools like valgrind better detect memory 
    problems.

Usage
    1. change your present work directory to nginx source directory
       $ cd (your nginx source directory).
    2. $ git clone git://github.com/shrimp/no-pool-nginx.git
    3. $ cd no-pool-nginx
    4. $ ./build
    5. then cofigure and make your nginx source.

